<sys_ui_theme action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
<active>true</active>
<css>/* Header Colors */
/* Search text color */ 
$search-text-color: #FFCC00 
/* Topbar background color*/
$navpage-header-bg: #4B116F
/* Topbar text color */
$navpage-header-color: #FFCC00 
/* Bottom border color on topbar */ 
$navpage-header-divider-color: #FFCC00 

/* Left nav and navigation toolbar background color */
/* Navigator hover color */
$nav-highlight-main: #fff
/* Background for expanded navigation items */
$subnav-background-color: #4B116F
/* Backgorund for navigator (left side only). */
$navpage-nav-bg: #4B116F
/* Background for Favorites list, history list, and Connect list background. */
$navpage-nav-bg-sub: #4B116F
/* Text color in main navigation */
$navpage-nav-color-sub: #FFCC00 
/* Text color when hovering over items in main nav */
$navpage-nav-mod-text-hover: #FFCC00 
/* Divider color in Navigator */
$nav-hr-color: #FFCC00 

/* Navigator tabs */
/* Active nav item underneath search */
$nav-highlight-bar-active: #FFCC00 
/* Inactive nav items underneath search */
$nav-highlight-bar-inactive: #FFCC00 
/* Background for currently selected navigation item underneath search */
$navpage-nav-selected-bg: #FFCC00 
/* Color of icon for currently active nav item. */
$navpage-nav-selected-color: #4B116F
/* Color of icons for non inactive nav items.*/
$navpage-nav-unselected-color: #FFCC00 

/* Navigator Application text */
/* Color for latest connect messages in right bar. */
$connect-latest-message: #FFCC00 
/* Timestamp header backgrounds in History tab*/
$nav-timeago-header-color: #fff
/* Core content text color */
$navpage-nav-app-text: #FFCC00 ;font-weight: bold;
/* Cpre content text color hover*/
$navpage-nav-app-text-hover: #4B116F;font-weight: bold;

/* Color of outline for search */
$navpage-nav-border: #FFCC00 
/* Default button/icon colors */
$navpage-button-color:  #FFCC00 
/* Hover color for ^^^ */
$navpage-button-color-hover: #FFCC00 
</css>
